# 🌍 IP Location Tracker

A simple Python script that lets you enter any IP address and fetches its **city, region, country, ISP, and timezone** details using a free public API.

---

## 🧠 Features

- 🔎 Tracks IP location instantly  
- 🌐 Shows city, region, country, and ISP  
- ⚡ Uses a **free API** (no API key required)  
- 🪶 Lightweight and beginner-friendly  

---

## 🧩 How It Works

This project uses the [`ip-api`](http://ip-api.com) service to fetch geolocation data for any IPv4 or IPv6 address.

