## 🛠️ Installation

1. **Clone the repository** (or download the script):

   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/ip-location-tracker.git
   cd ip-location-tracker

2. install dependencies:
    pip install requests

3. run this script:
   python ip_tracker.py

